<h1>How it works</h1>

<div class="center" id="explanation">
  <ul id="about">
    <li><h2>Sign up with an email address and username</h2></li>
    <li><h2>Start exchanging thoughts</h2></li>
    <li><h2>See other great exchanges</h2></li>
    <li><h2>Share thoughts with your friends</h2></li>
